<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2em; background-color: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
  <div class="container" style="border-top: 5px solid rgb(255, 124, 0); border-bottom: 5px solid rgb(255, 124, 0); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px 40px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 10px;">
    <div class="header" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
    </div>
    <p>Hello there!</p>
    <div class="message" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
      <p>We understand that passwords can be forgettable. No worries, though! We're here to help you get back into your account.</p>
      <p>To start the password reset process, simply click the button below:</p>
      <p>
      <%= link_to t('.password_change_link'), edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token, config: message['client-config'].to_s, redirect_url: message['redirect-url'].to_s).html_safe, style: "display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; margin-bottom: 1em; background-color: rgb(1, 84, 162); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;" %>
      </p>
    </div>
    <p>If you didn't initiate this password reset or no longer need it, you can safely disregard this email. For any concerns, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
    <p>Thank you for being a valued user of tracky.be.</p>
    <div class="footer" style="text-align: center; color: #888888; margin-top: 2em;">
      <p><a href="mailto:alexander.claes10@gmail.com" style="color: #888888; font-weight: 700;">Contact us via mail</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>
